pageProduct.name: Thompson's One-a-day Celery Seed 5000mg 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's One-A-Day Celery 5000mg is Traditionally used in
Western herbal medicine to help relieve mild arthritis and symptoms of gout.

Thompson's One-A-Day Celery is formulated with Celery Seed which has traditionally been used in Western herbal medicine to help relieve mild arthritic symptoms such as mild joint inflammation. Celery Seed has also traditionally been used in Western herbal medicine to help relieve symptoms of gout and as a diuretic to assist normal fluid balance.

Size: 60 capsules

Oil-Free?: Yes

KEY FEATURES

• Traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to help relieve mild arthritic symptoms such as mild joint inflammation
• Used in Western herbal medicine to help relieve symptoms of gout
• Used in Western herbal medicine as
a diuretic to assist normal fluid balance.
• Vegetarian/Vegan friendly
• One a day formula.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your health professional. If fluid retention or other symptoms persist, consult your health professional.

CAUTION

Keep out of reach of children.
Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains: Herbal extract equiv. to dry:
Apium graveolens (Celery) seed 5g (5000mg)

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap and recycle glass

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
